        </div>
      </nav>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h2>Enter the Myth</h2>
        <p>A fairytale not for children ‚Äì but for the wild-hearted, the thoughtful, the lost and free.</p>
        <a class="btn" href="#world">Explore the World</a>
