          <p>‚ÄúFreedom isn‚Äôt escape. It‚Äôs choosing to stay where truth hurts.‚Äù</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p>‚ÄúNot all monsters hide under beds. Some wear your smile.‚Äù</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      ¬© 2025 Fishnini. Dream boldly, walk softly.
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>
